          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-1" n="1">With a whirl of thought opprest</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-2" n="2">I sunk from Reverie to Rest</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-3" n="3">a Horrid Vision seiz'd my head</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-4" n="4">I saw the Graves yawn up their Dead</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-5" n="5">Iove arm'd with terrors burst the skies</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-6" n="6">and Thunder roars, and Lightning flies</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-7" n="7">amaz'd confus'd it's fate unknown</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-8" n="8">The World stood trembling round his throne</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-9" n="9">While Each Pale Sinner hung his head</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-10" n="10">Iove Nodding shook the heavns and said</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-11" n="11">`Offending Race of human kind</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-12" n="12">`By Nature Custom Learning blind</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-13" n="13">`You who thro frailty stepd aside</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-14" n="14">`and You who never err'd thro Pride</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-15" n="15">`and You whom Diffrent Sects have sham'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-16" n="16">`and come to see each other Damn'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-17" n="17">`So some Folks told you, but they knew,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-18" n="18">`no more of Iove's designs than You</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-19" n="19">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-20" n="20">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-21" n="21">`I to such Blockheads set my Wit</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-578-451O-line-22" n="22">`I damn such Fools! Go Go, you're bit────</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
